New Pacwyn 21 is here - it's a pack opener game you must to try right now! You will get unbelieveble experience playing our game.

Amazing pack opening system, a lot of squad building challenges, exclusive objectives and achievements - there is everything for you in the game.

Improve your squad day by day, play matches with opponents from over the world, win amazing rewards in a big number of modes and become the best Pacwyn player.

Playing Pacwyn Football Draft and Pack Opener you can:
1. Complete different collections of your favourite football players;
2. Join association/clans with your friends, participate in association tournaments and win big rewards;
3. Open regular packs, lightning rounds. We make a lot of fantastic pack opening events;
4. Build drafts to try different tactics in the matches;
5. Complete Objectives and receive unique achievements;
6. Play Weekend Tournaments to move to TOP 1 in the WorldWide Leaderboard;
7. Building squads and playing online matches against the opponents;
8. Trade with others users for more stuff;
9. Play daily mini-games to get even more rewards.

Pacwyn 21 has a great community of users, join us right now and find new friends!

This application’s sole purpose is to help its users learn how to build the best drafts and squads, find out more about football players and updates. This application is not endorsed by or affiliated with Electronic Arts Inc or other incorporations. All trademarks and copyrights belong to their respective owners.
